Package: future
Version: 0.4.2-9000
Title: The Future of R
Imports:
  listenv,
  globals
Suggests:
  R.rsp
VignetteBuilder:
  R.rsp
Authors@R: c(person("Henrik", "Bengtsson", role=c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
                                          email = "henrikb@braju.com"))
Description: A Future API for R.  The purpose of this package is to provide a very lightweight interface for using futures in R.  Except from a "lazy future", actual implementation of futures is done by other packages enhancing this package.
License: Private for now [will become LGPL (>= 2.1) when published]
LazyLoad: TRUE
URL: https://github.com/HenrikBengtsson/future
BugReports: https://github.com/HenrikBengtsson/future/issues
